# Devenv-driven dev shell.
#
# Note: we deliberately avoid `use devenv`, whose `devenv direnv-export` path
# segfaults on devenv 2.1.2 / macOS. `devenv print-dev-env` produces the same
# environment via plain shell exports without the crash.

watch_file devenv.nix devenv.yaml devenv.lock devenv.local.nix
eval "$(devenv print-dev-env 2>/dev/null)"
